it.unipi.dii.lsmsd.pokeMongo.userInterface

Class PokeScene

  • java.lang.Object
    • it.unipi.dii.lsmsd.pokeMongo.userInterface.PokeScene
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    PokeSceneWithHeader, PokeSceneWithTitle

    public class PokeScene
extends java.lang.Object
    PokeScene is the root class of the scene classes, a new scene must extends this one or one of its children. The class contains all the fundamental attributes, that are needed in all the scene classes.
